branchCategory.name: Rodless Cylinder CY3R-N, Magnetically Coupled Direct Mount w/o Switch Rail
branchCategory.description: <p>The CY3R Cylinder - Magnetically Coupled uses industrial strength magnets located in the piston and external carriage to form a single unit that will travel when actuated with air pressure.  The CY3R series has resin based lube retainers installed on the dust seal to more evenly distrubute lubricant for a reduction in minimum operating pressure.  70% longer wear rings will distribute a side load over a larger contact area for improved bearing performance.  <span style="color: #ff0000;">Please note the CY3R-N must be used with an external guide to support the load.</span></p>
